Last night the Board of Education approved its 2020-2021 budget.

We continue to spend responsibly to prioritize our students:

üñ§Acquiring New Land Adjacent to High School
üíõSpartan Stadium Renovation
üñ§New Spartan School of Art Academy
üíõMore Reading Resources for our youngest students
üñ§7 New School Buses
üíõRenovation of HS Library for New Sharon
üñ§New Marching Band Uniforms
üíõNew Paving at High School
üñ§Relocation of HS Weight Room
üíõTechnology & Maintenance Upgrades

All this is in addition to upgraded & new facilities and increased efficiencies from the Spartan Improvement Plan.

This testing site is by appointment only and open only to first responders: front-line healthcare workers, members of law enforcement, fire personnel, paramedics, & EMTs.

Hours of operation are 8:00 AM - 1:00 PM on select days.

First responders can make an appointment online by visiting: https://njpba.adlabscovidtest.com/
